               <msContents>
                  <summary>Images and Hymns to Saint Raguel, መልክአ፡ ራጉኤል፡; Asmat Prayers; Asmat prayer of the Seven Archangels, ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡; Asmat Prayer for Love and Peace, ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡ ወሰላም፡; Asmat prayer against the evil eye with the story of Jesus and the disciples at the Sea of Tiberias, ጸሎተ፡ ንድራ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="8r" facs="005">Fols 1r–8r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3085RepCh365">Hymn to Raguel the
                                                  Archangel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡ ወአጋንንት፡ ‎‎ራጉኤል፡ እንህል፡ እንህል፡ እንህል፡ ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ወለስእርተ፡ ‎‎ርእስከ፡ ኤጤሚሶር፡ ለርእስከ፡ ሰላም፡ ፍልድማሶር፡‎<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <locus from="8v" to="11v" facs="013">Fols 8v–11v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3085RepCh365">Hymn to Raguel the
                                                  Archangel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ዝክረ፡ ስመ፡ አብ፡ ኅብዕት። ወሞገሰ፡ ኄራን፡ ‎‎ነገሥት። ራጉኤል፡ መልአክ፡ ወሀቤ፡ ፯ ሀብታት። ጸግወኒ፡ ስመ፡ ‎‎በአስተብርኮ፡ ወስመ፡ ኬንያ፡ ኤላት። በጸውዖ፡ ስምከ፡ ኅቡዕ፡ አካዕ፡ ‎‎ቤቃ፡ ጼቃ፡<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus from="12r" to="23v" facs="016">Fols 12r–23v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3085RepCh365">Hymn to Raguel the
                                                  Archangel</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>At various points the scribe incorporates images to the Trinity and to Saint Michael, and then continues into the next prayer</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus from="24r" to="30r" facs="028">Fols 24r–30r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against the enemy, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡ ዝ፡ ውእቱ፡ ‎‎አስማተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ማኅተም፡ ዘወልድ፡ ጸጋ፡ ዘ ተውህበ፡ ለአሕዛብ፡ ‎‎ይኩነኒ፡ ዓቃቤ፡ ወረዳኤ፡ ሀብተ፡ ጸጋ፡ ወመዊዕ፡ ኃይል፡ አድኅነኒ፡‎<gap reason="omitted"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>This continues into the next work</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                     <locus from="30r" to="31v" facs="034">Fols 30r–31v</locus>
                     <title>Hymn to Raguel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ራጉኤል፡ ግሩም፡ መትልወ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሥዩም፡…።</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <locus from="32v" to="35v" facs="037">Fols 32v–35v</locus>
                     <title>Continuation of asmat prayer against the enemy, <locus target="#ms_i4">fol. ms_i4</locus>, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መግረሬ፡ ፀር፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <locus from="37r" to="41v" facs="041">Fols 37r–41v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer of the Seven Archangels, Dǝrsanä Zäsäbatu Liqǝnä Mäla’kǝt, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ድርሳን፡ ዘሰባቱ፡ ሊቃነ፡ መላእክት፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

