                  </msItem>

                </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                     <locus from="41v" to="43v" facs="046">Fols 41v–43v</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3085RepCh365">Hymn to Raguel the
                                                  Archangel</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለተፈንዎትከ፡ ዘአኮ፡ ለመዓት። ዳዕሙ፡ ለምሕረት።</incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>incorporated with asmat prayer</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                     <locus from="47r" to="53r" facs="051">Fols 47r–53r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for wealth and against the enemy, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ኃብት፡ ወመግረሬ፡ ፀር።</foreign>, incorporating Image of John, Son of Thunder, Mälk‘a Yoḥannǝs Wäldä Nägwädǝgwad, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡</foreign>, and the Image of the Trinity, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎በስመ፡ እብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ኃብት፡ ‎‎ወመግረሬ፡ ፀር። አስማት፡ ዘነገሮ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ‎‎ወልደ፡ ነጐድጓድ፡ እንዘ፡ ሀሎ፡ በገነት፡ ከመ፡ ይዕቀብ፡ ሥጋሃ፡ ‎‎ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ድንግል፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ እንዘ፡ ይብል።‎<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i10">
                     <locus from="53r" to="55r" facs="057">Fols 53r–55r</locus>
                     <title>Prayer for the reading of the <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2384Taamme">Taʾammǝra
                                                  Māryām</title>, and reading from the <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                     </title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i11">
                     <locus from="56r" to="67r" facs="060">Fols 56r–67r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer for Love and Peace, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡ ወሰላም፡</foreign>
                     </title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">‎በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡<gap reason="omitted"/> አአትብ፡ ገጽየ፡ ወኵለንታየ፡ በትእምርተ፡ ‎‎መስቀል፡ ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡ ወሰላም፡ ከመ፡ አቡነ፡ ዳዊት፡ ‎‎ወሰሎሞን። በርሃ፡ ፯ጨ፡ ፯ ላሃ፡‎<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i12">
                     <locus from="69r" to="72r" facs="073">Fols 69r–72r</locus>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer"> Asmat prayer against the evil eye with the story of Jesus and the disciples at the Sea of Tiberias, Ṣälota Nǝdra, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎተ፡ ንድራ፡</foreign></title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                     </incipit>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
